msgctxt "5548"
msgid ""
"困ったことになった。\n"
"せっかくの志の品なのに\n"
"さっぱり見方がわからん……"
msgstr ""
"I was in trouble. I don't know how to look at it even though it's a product "
"of my ambition ..."

msgctxt "5622"
msgid ""
"どうした、じいさん。\n"
"何の見方がわからないんだ？"
msgstr "What's wrong, grandfather. What do you see?"

msgctxt "5671"
msgid ""
"え？　いやその……\n"
"実は、「地球儀」の見方なのです。"
msgstr "e? No ... Actually, it's a view of a \"globe.\""

msgctxt "5724"
msgid "地球儀？"
msgstr "globe?"

msgctxt "5733"
msgid ""
"ええ……　ワシは寺子屋を開いている者です。\n"
"それが先日、子供たちの親御さんが金を出し合って\n"
"地球儀を寄付してくれましてな。"
msgstr ""
"Yeah ... I'm the one who opens the Terakoya. The other day, the parents of "
"the children donated money to donate the globe."

msgctxt "5856"
msgid ""
"ぜひ、この世界のことを地球儀で解説して\n"
"子供たちの見聞を広げてやってほしいと。"
msgstr ""
"By all means, I would like you to explain this world with a globe and "
"broaden your children's perspectives."

msgctxt "5935"
msgid ""
"地球儀か……\n"
"そういや俺も昔、\n"
"親っさんに見せてもらったことがあったな。"
msgstr "It's a globe ... No, I used to have my parents show me."

msgctxt "6008"
msgid ""
"え？　ではあなた、\n"
"地球儀の見方が判るということで？"
msgstr "e? So you know how to look at the globe?"

msgctxt "6061"
msgid "いや、まあ見たことがある程度のもんだが。"
msgstr "Well, I've seen it to some extent."

msgctxt "6102"
msgid ""
"いや！\n"
"それでもワシよりはよほどいい！\n"
"ワシなど地球儀は見るのも初めてで！"
msgstr ""
"Disagreeable! Still better than an eagle! It's the first time to see a globe"
" such as an eagle!"

msgctxt "6177"
msgid ""
"地球儀の解説なんてワシにはとても……\n"
"文字の読み書きくらいはなんとかなりますが\n"
"まったく困ってしまって。"
msgstr ""
"The explanation of the globe is very difficult for me ... I'm quite troubled"
" with reading and writing letters."

msgctxt "6282"
msgid "だったら素直にそう言やあいいだろう。"
msgstr "If so, I would say that honestly."

msgctxt "6319"
msgid ""
"それができれば苦労せんよ！\n"
"地球儀がどれだけ高いものか知ってますか？"
msgstr ""
"If you can do that, you won't have a hard time! Do you know how expensive "
"the globe is?"

msgctxt "6388"
msgid ""
"……親御さんたちは無邪気に\n"
"ワシがなんでも知っている物知りの老人と\n"
"決めつけてます。"
msgstr ""
"...... Parents innocently assume that I am an old man who knows everything."

msgctxt "6473"
msgid ""
"ワシが一言、「全然わからん」と言ったら\n"
"その瞬間、御厚意の地球儀がゴミと化すんですぞ！"
msgstr ""
"When I say \"I don't understand at all\", the globe of kindness turns into "
"garbage at that moment!"

msgctxt "6560"
msgid "なるほど。そういうことか……"
msgstr "I see. Is that so ..."

msgctxt "6589"
msgid ""
"……正直、適当に知ったかぶりして\n"
"でたらめに解説してしまおうかとも考えました。"
msgstr ""
"…… Honestly, I thought about giving a random explanation by pretending to "
"know it properly."

msgctxt "6668"
msgid ""
"ですがこの風雲の時代、\n"
"近い将来異国と戦争さえ起こりかねんのに\n"
"子供にでたらめを教えていいものか!?"
msgstr ""
"However, in this Fengyun era, is it okay to teach children bullshit even "
"though a war with a foreign country may occur in the near future !?"

msgctxt "6767"
msgid ""
"戦争に正確な地理的情報は必須です。\n"
"でたらめな知識で戦争に臨んでは\n"
"子供たちが無駄に命を落としかねない。"
msgstr ""
"Accurate geographical information is essential for war. Children can die in "
"vain if they face a war with random knowledge."

msgctxt "6872"
msgid "……一体、私はどうしたらいいんでしょう!?"
msgstr "...... What should I do !?"

msgctxt "6913"
msgid ""
"そこまで子供のことを思うなら、やはり\n"
"正直に言えばいいんじゃないか？"
msgstr "If you think about children that much, you should be honest."

msgctxt "6982"
msgid ""
"地球儀がゴミになろうが\n"
"でたらめ吹き込むよりはマシだろう。"
msgstr ""
"Whether the globe becomes garbage or not, it's better than blowing it in "
"randomly."

msgctxt "7041"
msgid ""
"いや、それはそれでワシが赤っ恥をかく。\n"
"下手すると生徒がみんないなくなってしまう。"
msgstr ""
"No, that's why I'm embarrassed. If you are not good at it, all the students "
"will disappear."

msgctxt "7124"
msgid "結局、自分が見栄はりたいだけじゃねえか……"
msgstr "After all, you just want to look good ..."

msgctxt "7167"
msgid ""
"でもあなたなら地球儀を解説できますな？\n"
"どうかお力を貸してもらえんでしょうか!?"
msgstr "But can you explain the globe? Could you please help me !?"

msgctxt "7246"
msgid "……寺子屋で俺が地球儀を解説するってことか？"
msgstr "...... Is it that I explain the globe at Terakoya?"

msgctxt "7291"
msgid ""
"簡単なところでいいんです！\n"
"今、日本に迫っている主な異国の位置とかだけでも\n"
"御存知ならなんとかサマになるから！"
msgstr ""
"It's good in an easy place! If you know only the location of the main "
"foreign countries that are approaching Japan now, you will be able to "
"manage!"

msgctxt "7402"
msgid ""
"お願いします！\n"
"これからうちの寺子屋に来ていただけませんか!?"
msgstr "Please! Would you please come to our Terakoya from now on !?"

msgctxt "7463"
msgid "いや、悪いが断る。"
msgstr "No, I refuse."

msgctxt "7482"
msgid ""
"そ、そうですか……\n"
"まあ無理な御相談でしたな。\n"
"見ず知らずの方に……"
msgstr ""
"Well, that's right ... Well, it was an impossible consultation. For "
"strangers ..."

msgctxt "7555"
msgid "わかった、いいだろう。"
msgstr "Okay, that's fine."

msgctxt "7578"
msgid ""
"あ、ありがとうございます！\n"
"さ、それでは早速こちらへ。"
msgstr "Oh, thank you! Well then, go here immediately."

msgctxt "8536"
msgid "寺子屋の先生"
msgstr "Terakoya teacher"

msgctxt "8685"
msgid "引き受ける"
msgstr "undertake"

msgctxt "8696"
msgid "断る"
msgstr "turn down"
